Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Car workers to strike
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf16
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Sep 1984
Strike calls as car company bosses pocket bonuses while the workers still suffer from pay cuts. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less